<subSubSection pageId="67" pageNumber="264" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="67.[151,1436,1697,1875]" pageId="67" pageNumber="264">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[196,273,1735,1761]" pageId="67" pageNumber="264">Notes.</emphasis>
The presence of this species in Sardinia is documented neither in the examined collections nor in the literature (Tab. 1), except for the erroneous record by 
<bibRefCitation author="Holdhaus, K." box="[836,1037,1773,1799]" pageId="67" pageNumber="264" pagination="1 - 199" refId="ref73722" refString="Holdhaus, K. (1924) Das Tyrrhenisproblem - Zoogeographische Untersuchungen unter besonderer Berucksichtigung der Koleopteren. Annalen des Naturhistorischen Museums in Wien, 37, 1 - 199." type="journal article" year="1924">Holdhaus (1924)</bibRefCitation>
, the source of which is unknown. The species is cited from nearby 
<collectingCountry box="[552,641,1811,1837]" name="France" pageId="67" pageNumber="264">Corsica</collectingCountry>
(
<emphasis box="[660,690,1811,1836]" italics="true" pageId="67" pageNumber="264">cf.</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Mazur, S." box="[699,848,1811,1837]" pageId="67" pageNumber="264" refId="ref74858" refString="Mazur, S. (2004) Histeridae. In: Lobl, I. &amp; Smetana, A. (Eds), Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera, Volume 2. Hydrophiloidea - Staphylinoidea. Apollo Books, Stenstrup, pp. 68 - 102." type="book" year="2004">Mazur 2004</bibRefCitation>
), but it is foreign to the Italian fauna (
<emphasis box="[1313,1342,1811,1836]" italics="true" pageId="67" pageNumber="264">cf.</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Vienna, P." pageId="67" pageNumber="264" refId="ref76703" refString="Vienna, P. (1980) Fauna d'Italia XVI. Coleoptera Histeridae. Calderini, Bologna, 373 pp." type="book" year="1980">Vienna 1980</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
